query:
INSERT INTO
                trips_to_trips_types (trip_id, trip_type_id)
            (SELECT trips.id as trip_id, trips_types.id as trip_type_id
                FROM trips
                INNER JOIN trips_types ON true
                WHERE
                    trips.id = $1
                    AND trips.user_id = $2
                    AND trips_types.id = $3
                    AND trips_types.user_id = $4)
